data.description: Now's your chance for a piece of Twiggs County Paradise! This cozy 3 bed 2 bath home has all the privacy you need and hillside pond view. Level back yard and plenty of room for and out building or a garden. Enjoy evenings on the front or back porch. Large kitchen for entertaining with open design that overlooks the living room. Separate laundry room near the rear entry. The master bedroom has a spacious closet and roomy bathroom with garden tub. Nestled in the country but convenient to Macon or Gordon.
